review_data: Reviewed in the United States on April 7, 2023
name: Mark S
title: Great telescoping roasting sticks
review: These 10 roasting sticks came just in time for my daughter's outdoor bonfire party.Colored wooden handles make it easy for anyone to recognize their own stick.The telescoping feature was definitely the best and can extend out to 32 inches which definitely provides enough distance from bonfires.But it also can shorten to just 1 foot long and you can skewer food on a grill or stove top as well.The wooden handle is easy to grab and prevents the heat conduction.But it's a perfect accompaniment for fire pit parties.FYI, I think the cleaning aspect depends on what you're cooking (i.e. marshmallows are always going to be hard to wipe off).

review: These do what they do. They are expandable which is nice. I like the quantity of sticks in this package. It was the right about for my bonfire party. title: Marshmallow time

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2023
name: BlueSkys
title: Bought to Replace Old Roasting Sticks
review: I bought these to replace some older roasting sticks that I had. My old ones did not telescope and they were hard to store and wash. These sticks are really easy to wash and are easy to store in the storage bag that was provided. Once stored they don’t take up much room at all. I hang them on the coat rack in our storage closet. I love how they are color coded so that the pickier people can have their own stick and don’t have to share with anyone else. They are sturdy enough to be able to roast 2 hot dogs at a time. Overall I am very pleased.
